Keyboard Management Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides keyboard handling and avoidance system for mobile applications.
Implements keyboard appearance detection, content adjustment, and input field
management optimized for mobile keyboard interactions.

Key Features:
- Keyboard appearance/dismissal detection
- Content adjustment for keyboard
- Input field scrolling and focusing
- Keyboard height calculation
- Keyboard type optimization
- Auto-correction and suggestions
- Keyboard toolbar management
- Return key handling
- Input accessory view support
- Keyboard animation synchronization
- Cross-platform keyboard support
- Accessibility keyboard support

Provides complete keyboard management system for building mobile applications
with proper keyboard handling and user input experience.
:End Note

